title: Affordable Living - Wonderful Floor Plans for Every Budget! Call Now!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'At Elm Creek we have apartments with a luxury feel at affordable prices!', 'This conveniently located community is nestled next to the Elm Creek Regional Park.', 'You will enjoy the secluded feel of your new quiet home, but still minutes from downtown Minneapolis.', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Pet-Friendly Community', '- Water, Sewer, Heat & Trash Removal Service Included In Rent!', '- Generous Bedroom Closet Space', '- Professional On-Site Management', '- Open & Spacious Floorplans', '- Fully Equipped Community Kitchen', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'ElmCreek participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Saturday:10:00AM-2:00PM', 'Make the move today by giving our professional staff a call:', 'show contact info', 'Elmcreek Apartments', '11719 Champlin Drive', 'Champlin, MN, 55316', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', '9Ys5SMpm']
